text: Swindon Town F.C. are an English football club. They are based in Swindon and play in Football League One. They play their home games at the County Ground. ==League position== Season League Position 2000/01 Second Division 20th 2001/02 Second Division 13th 2002/03 Second Division 10th 2003/04 Second Division 5th 2004/05 League One 12th 2005/06 League One 23rd 2006/07 League Two 3rd 2007/08 League One 13th 2008/09 League One 15th ===Former position=== Category:English football clubs Category:Swindon Category:1879 establishments in England
